    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. It has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, with every aspect of the car\u2014from the flawless paintwork to the pristine interior\u2014showing no signs of wear or age. All original documentation and service records are included, confirming its history of expert care and minimal usage. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that drives and looks like a brand-new car.",
      "price": 49500.0,
